<HEADLINE> London Shares Close Lower  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   LONDON (AP) -- Share prices fell on the London Stock Exchange on
Thursday.
</P>
<P>
   The Financial Times-Stock Exchange 100-Share Index closed down
56.3 points, or 0.9 percent, at 6,241.2.
</P>
<P>
   Provisional market volume was 1.2 billion shares, down from 1.7
billion on Wednesday.
</P>
